  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function add_layer_snippet(layer: Number(gint), snippet: <link xref="Cogl.Snippet">Cogl.Snippet</link>): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for cogl_pipeline_add_layer_snippet()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Adds a shader snippet that will hook on to the given layer of the
pipeline. The exact part of the pipeline that the snippet wraps
around depends on the hook that is given to
<link xref="Cogl.Snippet.new"/>. Note that some hooks can't be used with a layer
and need to be added with <link xref="Cogl.Pipeline.add_snippet"/> instead.</p>
  <p>Since 1.10</p>
